<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">丰</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson03144dc0eac6">
子之丰兮，俟我乎巷兮，悔予不送兮。<br />子之昌兮，俟我乎堂兮，悔予不将兮。<br />衣锦褧衣，裳锦褧裳。叔兮伯兮，驾予与行。<br />裳锦褧裳，衣锦褧衣。叔兮伯兮，驾予与归。
</div>
</div>
